<para style="q1">

<verse number="16" style="v" />But may all those who seek you rejoice and be glad in you;</para>

<para style="q1">let everyone who loves your salvation say continually,</para>

<para style="q1">"May Yahweh be praised."</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="17" style="v" />I am poor and needy;</para>

<para style="q1">yet the Lord thinks about me.</para>

<para style="q1">You are my help and you come to my rescue;</para>

<para style="q1">do not delay, my God.</para>
